    "media:imagetext": "NE\nNORTHEAST\nComplete System Timetable Effective April 30, 1972\n2 ways\nto fly to\nMiami/ Fl. Lauderdale\nand back for\n$100.\nRound-trip Coach air fare.\nFederal tax included.\nFrom Boston, New York, Philadelphia,\nHartford or Baltimore\nWeekend\nLeave riday oi\nSaturday, return\nSunday or Monday\nof the same weekend.\n$50 for children\nunder 12.\n2.\nMidweek\nTravel on luesdays,\nWednesdays or Thursdays\nin boin directions\nand stay at least\n5 days but no more\nthan 2l days.\n$50 for children\nunder 12.\nThese fares are available between\nBoston, Philadelphia and Tampa too!\nSTO in July and August\n2005. 133.034 (20)",
